ed and modulated making them the ideal candidates for a variety of plasmonic\ndevices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Jun 2020 18:04:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 22 Jun 2020 14:52:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-01"}
