ensitive data; (5) in\nthe majority of cases, Covid-related apps are released by entities with past\nexperience on the market, mostly official government entities or public health\norganizations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 Jun 2020 08:02:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 15 Jan 2021 10:04:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-18"}
