 tackled from\nprovider side to reduce overall energy demand at the user side; one of which is\nsetting a low resolution as default.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 Jun 2020 13:38:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-22"}
